summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from G. Debritz and Debrits, his wife, and Eliza Askneim, to the City of Seattle, dated the 26th day of July, 1907, to Lots Seven (7) and Nine 99) in Block Nine (9) and Lots Three (3), Eight (8), Seven (7) and Nine (9), Block Eleven (11) all in Craven's Division to Green Lake Addition in the City of Seattle.
